6月26日，天气图显示[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]最西北角有热带风暴存在<ref name="Partagas">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1898-1900/1899_1.pdf | title = Year 1899 | author = Jose F. Partagas | date = 1996 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080924040636/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1898-1900/1899_1.pdf | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | pages = 39–53 | accessdate = 2016-12-06 | location = Miami, Florida | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2008-09-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋起初的持续风速为每小时65公里，在向西北方向前进期间强度基本保持不变。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月27日上午9点，风暴以风力时速65公里强度从[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]最西南角[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。三小时后，气旋减弱成热带低气压，再于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}下午18点在德克萨斯州东南部上空消散。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>风暴在[[胡德县_(德克萨斯州)|胡德县]][[格兰伯里_(德克萨斯州)|格兰伯里]]（{{lang|en|Granbury}}）至[[韦科_(德克萨斯州)|韦科]]降下暴雨，对该州沿海地区已经发生的洪灾雪上加霜<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-12-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161201044253/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | deadurl = no | format = PDF | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | title = Texas Hurricane History | author = David M. Roth | date = 2010-01-17 | work = Weather Prediction Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | pages = 28, 29 | accessdate = 2016-12-06 | location = Camp Springs, Maryland }}</ref>。据州参议员阿斯伯里·巴斯科姆·戴维森（{{lang|en|Asbury Bascom Davidson}}）所述，[[布拉索斯河|布拉索斯河]]、[[科罗拉多河_(德克萨斯州)|科罗拉多河]]、[[瓜达卢佩河_(德克萨斯州)|瓜达卢佩河]]、[[纳瓦索塔河|纳瓦索塔河]]及[[圣萨巴河|圣萨巴河]]泛滥成灾<ref name="Partagas" />，估计有3.1万平方公里陆地被淹。[[罗伯森县_(德克萨斯州)|罗伯森县]][[赫恩_(德克萨斯州)|赫恩]]（{{lang|en|Hearne}}）的降雨量超过所有雨量计的最高刻度。全州有数千人无家可归，洪灾共夺走284条人命，损失总额达900万美元。<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161029003207/http://lifeonthebrazosriver.com/Floods.htm | archivedate = 2016-10-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://lifeonthebrazosriver.com/Floods.htm | title = Floods of the Brazos River in Texas | publisher = LifeOnTheBrazosRiver.com | accessdate = 2016-12-06 | date =  }}</ref>
